    AbstractProcessPluginDefinition
    Implements AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getName(), AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getVersion(), AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getReleaseDate(), AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getTitle(), AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getPublisher() and AbstractProcessPluginDefinition.getPublisherEmail() based on properties defined in a "plugin.properties" file.
    ProcessPluginApi
    Gives access to services available to process plugins.
    ProcessPluginDefinition
    A provider configuration file named "dev.dsf.ProcessPluginDefinition" containing the canonical name of the class implementing this interface needs to be part of the process plugin at "/META-INF/services/".
